    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Arguably one of the most important pieces of equipment to get you from A to B and beyond, think about the wear-and-tear we put our bags through; stuffed into overhead bins, squeezing into tight corners, thrown, tossed and bursting at the seams due to that last minute packing choices. Quality and durability is key to a backpack’s longevity and performance, which you will find in this hiking backpack by ASR Outdoor. Meet the ASR Outdoor 30L Gold Panning large backpack. It is functional, durable, has a large capacity and designed in classic rucksack style. It will quickly become your go-to pack for everything from overnight hiking trips to long-haul air travel</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 30L Day Excursion Backpack High Capacity Gold Prospecting Rucksack</h2>\n  <p>Arguably one of the most important pieces of equipment to get you from A to B and beyond, think about the wear-and-tear we put our bags through; stuffed into overhead bins, squeezing into tight corners, thrown, tossed and bursting at the seams due to that last minute packing choices. Quality and durability is key to a backpack’s longevity and performance, which you will find in this hiking backpack by ASR Outdoor.</p>\n  <p>Meet the ASR Outdoor 30L Gold Panning large backpack. It is functional, durable, has a large capacity and designed in classic rucksack style. It will quickly become your go-to pack for everything from overnight hiking trips to long-haul air travel.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>30L HIKING BACKPACK:</strong> Carry everything you need and easily access all of it; (1) large top load lid closure with interior draw cord closure; (3) exterior compartments with magnetic snaps</li>\n    <li><strong>FIELD TESTED &amp; RESPECTED:</strong> Reinforced double stiching across all seams and connection points; side pockets feature magnetic snap closures with zipper; adjustable chest strap provides comfort, as well as a top carry handle for easy maneuvering and lifting</li>\n    <li><strong>GREAT FOR GOLD PANNING EQUIPMENT:</strong> Easily fit all your gold prospecting equipment; aluminum folding sluice box, gold pans, classifier screens and other small tools, you can trek it all in one go to your claim</li>\n    <li><strong>QUALITY CANVAS FABRIC:</strong> Made from cotton, this backpack is built to last; breathable, natural fiber cotton won’t irritate skin, is of better quality and more durable than other synthetic fabrics; machine washable (hang dry)</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Dimensions: 19.5 (H) x 12.5 (L) x 7 (W) inches; Weight: 1.86lbs; Color: Black, Brown, Khaki, or OD Green; Side Pocket Dimensions: 13 x 4 x 2.5 inches; Front Pouch Dimensions: 8 x 12&quot; x 2.5 inches; Capacity: 30L; Material: Cotton</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72751/hF52cKq1AUSehKycWf6kUSydKRcWG7-metaY2FudmFzX2JhY2twYWNrX3BhcmVudC5qcGc=-.jpg\" alt=\"Arguably one of the most important pieces of equipment to get you from A to B and beyond, think about the wear-and-tear we put our bags through;\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> CANBPBK</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 060886452409</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Extra Large</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>With 30 liters or 1830 cubic inches (volume) of packing space, the large central compartment of this rucksack can really hold it all. In addition to the huge central compartment, the rucksack features an interior draw cord compression closure, large top load lid closure, three exterior compartments and reinforced stitching throughout. Furthermore, all exterior side pockets feature both zipper and buckle closure, so you can rest assured your belongings will remain safe and secure. Lastly, adjustable carry straps provide comfort customization, as well as a top carry handle for easy maneuvering and lifting when needed. The canvas rucksack is made from 100% quality cotton, a natural, breathable and durable fiber that will perform better than other synthetic materials in the long run.</p>\n  <p>This backpack has been designed with gold panning and gold prospecting in mind. A great option for novice or experts alike, it will easily fit gold panning equipment like mini or folding sluice boxes, gold pans, sieves or classifiers and other small tools, so you can trek it all in one go to your field site. Built for adventure, reach for the ASR Outdoor 30L Gold Panning Hiking Backpack for your next camping trip, day hike, backpacking excursion and more.</p>\n  <p>Machine washable; air dry.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
